short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Toggle Hostinger ID boxes on a Hostinger webpage.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The Hostinger ID Finder is a handy tool designed to make the Hostinger web design process easier. The extension adds overlay boxes to your website, displaying the IDs of various elements. You can identify and manage the components of your Hostinger site, making designing and custom styles more accessible.
